latestPosts.caption:
Sunday Done Right!
Enjoyed the awesome “Sunday Brunch” at QEY
Starting with exquisite tapas like Caprese Burrata, Lamb Dolmas, and Shish Tuk, to the interactive cocktail-making session featuring a floral gin cocktail, every moment was delightful. 🍹✨
The main course took indulgence to the next level with Chicken Stroganoff, Seafood Paella, and perfectly cooked John Dory. 🐟 
The grand finale? Desserts that were pure decadence,Vanilla Panna Cotta, Chocolate torte and Baklava Cheesecake🍰
If you’re looking for the perfect mix of flavors, fun, and festive vibes, QEY is the place to be. 🍴💫 #SundayBrunchDoneRight #QEYExperience #MumbaiEats #LuxuryInfluencer #Food #Fashion #ShillpaKatariaSingh
